In article &lt;8804141838.AA10705@venera.isi.edu&gt; pvm@VENERA.ISI.EDU (Paul Mockapetris) writes:
&gt; prohibit "%" and "!" on the left hand side of the @

"%" and "!" are legal characters in mailbox names!  (Read rfc822 if you don't
believe me.)  I have been thinking about creating myself a mailbox with
the left hand side of "%" just to see how many mailers it would break.
